---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | William64.com" description="Privacy policy for William64.com - How we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-text border-b border-border pb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary">
      <p class="text-sm text-text-tertiary">Last updated: January 18, 2026</p>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>This website collects minimal information necessary for its operation:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Website analytics through aggregated, anonymized data</li>
          <li>Error logs for technical troubleshooting</li>
          <li>Contact information you voluntarily provide</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Improve website performance and user experience</li>
          <li>Respond to inquiries and messages</li>
          <li>Analyze traffic patterns for optimization</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Data Protection</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information, including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
          <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
          <li>Limited data collection and retention</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>This website may use third-party services such as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Content delivery networks (CDNs)</li>
          <li>Analytics services</li>
          <li>Font providers</li>
        </ul>
        <p>These services have their own privacy policies and data handling practices.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Know what personal information we collect</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
          <li>Opt-out of non-essential data collection</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website uses minimal cookies for essential functionality only. You can control cookie settings through your browser preferences.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For questions about this privacy policy or data handling practices:</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:william@william64.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover">william@william64.com</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text">Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Return to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>